# ── Daily Tool: your AI key ────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com and sign in.
#    Use a PERSONAL Gmail account (18+). Work/school Google accounts are
#    sometimes blocked by an administrator.
# 2. Accept the terms. Open "API Keys" from the dashboard.
# 3. Copy your key, then duplicate this file as `.env` and paste it below.
#
# The key is free (no credit card). It stays on the server side of this
# app and is never sent to the browser. After the workshop you can delete
# the key on the same AI Studio page.
#
# Heads up: free-tier prompts may be used by Google to improve its
# products. Don't paste anything personal or confidential.

GOOGLE_API_KEY=paste-your-key-here

# Optional: swap the model. Default is google/gemini-2.5-flash.
# MODEL=google/gemini-2.5-flash

# CopilotKit sends anonymous usage telemetry by default. Uncomment to opt out.
# COPILOTKIT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=true

# ── Deploying live to Cloudflare? ──────────────────────────────────────
#
# This .env file is for running the app on your own machine. To put the app
# live on the web, you do NOT use this file. The Deploy-to-Cloudflare button
# (see the README) asks you for your key in the browser and stores it as an
# encrypted Cloudflare Secret on your own Worker. The secret field names live
# in `.dev.vars.example`.

